M|Writ|desc|Processes data
M|Writ|tx|```
M|Writ|tx|```yaml  theme={null}
M|Writ|desc|Does stuff w/ files
M|Writ|tx|```
M|Prog|tx|SKILL.md serves as an overview that points Claude to detailed materials as needed, like a table of contents in an onboarding guide. For an explanation of how progressive disclosure works, see [How Skills work](/en/doc/ag-and-tools/ag-skills/overview#how-skills-work) in the overview.
M|Prog|**Pr|**
M|Prog|it|Keep SKILL.md body under 500 lines for optimal perf
M|Prog|it|Split cn into separate files when approaching this limit
M|Prog|it|Use the patterns below to organize instructions, code, and resources effectively
